channel.title: Comments on: Funny Food Lion Cartoon Signs

item.title: By: C S Stroh
item.dc:creator: C S Stroh
item.description: I would like to thank you for posting my humor. It was really fun and rewarding drawing those pictures. It is fascinating to see your own work pop up on the computer. Even when it is not your best work.
